{"tid":1667533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（裝飾）Fila 香港高層極深藍 罔顧員工安全","createTime":"2019-10-21T13:46:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T10:15:08.000Z","uid":195403,"like":286,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"3236419cfaffc431568c051481cb09e06998f5ed","tid":1667533,"uid":195403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T13:46:24.000Z","msg":"（裝飾）Fila 香港高層極深藍 罔顧員工安全<br />\n利申： 前Fila員工，幫舊同事開<br />\n<br />\n香港Fila比大陸安踏收購左好幾年，老細係紅底福建人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，總公司係廈門果邊，昨日柏麗大道、Isquare 拋哂TG出哂裝甲車水炮車 區經都仲要最前線同事落閘執倉繼續番工. 仲講明點都唔會比同事早走 明知再遲會冇哂交通  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n海港城好多同類型鋪頭4，5點9成都收哂 死城咁都唔比人早D走  <br />\n好多尖沙咀區同事要行到紅磡 先搵到車再轉車走<br />\n<br />\n跟住旺角區有粒TG拋正門口附近  大部分同事都索哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，成班防暴狗推進緊先肯落閘，之前有幾次都係有大量防暴狗係條街捉人、狗車封哂路又冇黨鐵先比落閘。<br />\n<br />\n禁員工聲，唔俾帶口罩返工。話我哋影響市容。又有店鋪高職位同事會扮黃想Chok 人有冇去發夢跟住篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n班高層係屋企睇就覺得冇事，好和平 但有冇諗下同事住得遠點番屋企？<br />\n班狗癲起上黎射橡膠彈/實彈誤中同事點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"ff2fc7c67a2a5de1dbd84ccd206b3928d6f00d26","tid":1667533,"uid":32883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:42:26.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"0bbae13a7b11a64e1457ff692929f03e04a99f8a","tid":1667533,"uid":9411,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:43:14.000Z","msg":"睇錯fifa"},{"pid":"4b56b5214b6301c4584347cce031f969798d7333","tid":1667533,"uid":153811,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:46:55.000Z","ms